{"tid":555200,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[又中打手伏]果套平安谷都叫好睇？","createTime":"2018-02-09T08:20:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T10:05:22.000Z","uid":74778,"like":9,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6d67d57013af96ceb4015779d6a99afb624a51d1","tid":555200,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T08:20:50.000Z","msg":"做左2，3集，都唔諗住睇，因為啱啱睇完好好笑既誇世代，<br />\n<br />\n比連登幾個打手post講到好好睇咁，又話咩少有深度劇，又話估唔到會做呢個題材，咁我又睇下<br />\n<br />\n我一睇已經做緊燒死陳瀅，咦，真係拍鬼估喎<br />\n<br />\n我屌佢老母，一集唔洗就同我講d鬼係人扮<br />\n<br />\n之後唔洗講已經一個鬼字都無再出現過，反而係做左古裝版既棟篤神探，集集就睇黃浩賢同陳凱琳查案<br />\n<br />\n初初都諗有樣野係無錯既，真係tvb少有既題材，又女權，又鼓勵自由，又講到受過西方教育會好聰明咁，一反親中形象，一路睇都幾刺激，形住第二日tvb d高層會比人拉柒曬。點知<br />\n<br />\n我屌佢老母，原來係抗日劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。已經唔撚想再係呢個標題講落去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講下拍攝手法同劇情<br />\n<br />\n我屌佢老母，我晚晚花1個鐘睇佢，佢比左8成廠景我，再唔係就係古裝街嘈交<br />\n<br />\n祠堂門口，吊死女人，全部係古裝街，我屌你咩，睇唔出咩？<br />\n<br />\n講開吊女人，劉江都唔知依鄉例吊左幾撚多次女人，又次次都比人救走，都係比同一班人救走，有無咁戇鳩既村長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n劇情唔合理，睇到保長用鐵鏈鎖住個老婆已經無乜心機睇落去，都唔撚合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"134b3525aa1d2be74b96f125a2d4b9870972bacc","tid":555200,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T08:22:47.000Z","msg":"啱啱又有post吹奏，真係忍唔住要講出黎<br />\n<br />\n係咪要話比大陸聽 香港人都話抗日劇好睇啊阿爺，可以入貨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8185f157be7ed2895705c64617b10bfb93edc488","tid":555200,"uid":167426,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T08:23:45.000Z","msg":"唔係話好好睇<br />\n但起碼好睇過誇世代，溏心風暴3同無間道呢堆垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7a44cd9e4b0e5d770beb755c19b59329dc464c0","tid":555200,"uid":74778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T08:25:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係話好好睇<br />\n但起碼好睇過誇世代，<span style=\"color: red;\">溏心風暴3同無間道</span>呢堆垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同意"},{"pid":"45a8d6042731433fe6b5ed26427640e4f0e7dd63","tid":555200,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T09:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7761b6fb5aec285d1ec977c4c5a91e332acdb5e1","tid":555200,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T09:42:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab42b36e1b473607f4506744e2eb1bd458ea2a74","tid":555200,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T09:43:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"badfdbf4b662ea0768a87cb8665b369a9c4d87c5","tid":555200,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T09:44:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31b26a05467a3c31b8533449aa96d09688ef2417","tid":555200,"uid":31151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T09:44:33.000Z","msg":"抗日？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a436d2ad8000325d1cf7ea8d4cb8eeded1092b0","tid":555200,"uid":38255,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"31b26a05467a3c31b8533449aa96d09688ef2417","tid":555200,"uid":31151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T09:44:33.000Z","msg":"抗日？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T09:56:27.000Z","msg":"邊到抗日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 堆山賊又食大鑊飯又全民大煉金，擺明影射緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後仲應該係國民政府打走山賊，政治極不正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>啱啱又有post吹奏，真係忍唔住要講出黎<br />\n<br />\n係咪要話比大陸聽 香港人都話抗日劇好睇啊阿爺，可以入貨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.synergynet.org.hk/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/2015062502.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.synergynet.org.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F06%2F2015062502.jpg&h=bd6be910&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/07/203337_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F07%2F203337_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=d7a28b55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/07/203343_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F07%2F203343_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=1050575b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/07/203347_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F07%2F203347_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=06ec195d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/07/203352_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F07%2F203352_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=597e4314&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/07/203421_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F07%2F203421_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=6573a01e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/07/203424_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F07%2F203424_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=9bd87eb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢夠膽咪入囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢幕有支那人都覺影射緊公民廣場，不過其他人自我安慰話佢多心姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n男權vs女權，實際係影射強權vs民權，雖然間接過誇世代直出2047核爆，但其實抽得仲入肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbc881d268ba174c5c0e89dc6b3e699fdbb19512","tid":555200,"uid":41508,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T10:04:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"49c9ea300a70f8d7881ec62738f4efd31bc48256","tid":555200,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T10:13:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e63fab1bab9dbf5e4dc36eb0ac10feac28c3520a","tid":555200,"uid":38255,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"dbc881d268ba174c5c0e89dc6b3e699fdbb19512","tid":555200,"uid":41508,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T10:04:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T10:47:14.000Z","msg":"一個叫周學民既老師同另一個女仔畀人綁起左，畀班唔講道理既男村民用鄉例處置，班學生睇唔過眼衝入祠堂前地保護佢兩個，但班學生繼續畀班野蠻男村民暴力對待，d女村民細路阿媽睇唔過眼終於覺醒想反男村民，最後大家推推撞撞炒埋一碟變到上面幅圖咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話係唔小心寫咁既劇情出黎都無人信啦，港豬c9同戲入面班女村民會開始識反都係因為細路。<br />\n<br />\n套戲d男村民舉動仲支那人劣根性刻畫得好傳神：割席，有錢唔得都變得；送個仔出外國讀書，自己繼續用舊果套強權管人；攞住支槍叫大家講道理；明明自己都係被欺壓果個，但就幫手去欺壓更低既人；讀最多書果個最無風骨下下都附和當權者；一講錢就反面，人地無左個孫就話一向係咁，自己無左個孫就一定要追究到底。都唔係一兩集係咁，成套戲一直都有班廢老叔父展示魯迅筆下吃人禮教，支那人既醜惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/09/184517_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F09%2F184517_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=f687eac6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/09/184536_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F09%2F184536_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=879275fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/09/184601_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F09%2F184601_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=83681c20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/09/184625_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F09%2F184625_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=0cd65dbb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9bab5688248895d240e1020f72307a79243f4f2","tid":555200,"uid":61660,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T10:53:48.000Z","msg":"呢套野俾我感覺係眼高手低版既火舞黃沙就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f261977d4f1dd45c71e6c07202926e5271d2cbe2","tid":555200,"uid":38255,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c9bab5688248895d240e1020f72307a79243f4f2","tid":555200,"uid":61660,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T10:53:48.000Z","msg":"呢套野俾我感覺係眼高手低版既火舞黃沙就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T11:06:34.000Z","msg":"初初青蘭自焚果段真係好好睇，<br />\n去到初一惟明北杏畀人綁起果段都仲好正，之後查立秋單案開始慢，仲多左好多笑料氣氛緩和左（雖則係烘托水雄呢個角色），最失望就係女人開始覺醒反果段開始，好似畀人剪左好多咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由零到完全覺醒sharp一聲既事，有d野舖左線但竟然無左件事。最後山賊呢段雖然無大反駁位但一集爆晒出黎好暴走feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d537d1f37fda29a0a8399168560f7f7230cd8a46","tid":555200,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T11:21:42.000Z","msg":"Tvb劇睇完就算啦<br